Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:23.63,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Da ist er.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:33.86,Default,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,Er lebt noch, oder?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:34.61,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:37.01,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:38.37,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Fangen wir an.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:42.34,Default,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Moanday?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:43.46,Default,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:44.28,Default,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Tuesday!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:45.38,Default,Itadori,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.38,0:23:46.73,Default,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Weddonesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:47.48,Default,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:48.81,Default,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Verarsch mich nicht!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:50.03,Default,Itadori,0000,0000,0000,,Nächstes Mal: „Schwankungen“.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:56.62,TypePlaceholder,Type,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman Bold\fsp1\c&HFAFAFA&\bord3\blur3\pos(320,105)\3c&H000000&}Nächstes Mal\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs+5}Schwankungen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:51.96,Default,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wer hat sich diese\NSchreibweise ausgedacht?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:54.62,Default,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Jemand, der schlauer ist als du.

